entries.source: If enabled beta plugins will be automatically enabled after installtion by default. Note: you can toggle this on and off for each plugin in the "Add Plugin" form.
entries.translated: 如果启用测试版插件将在安装后自动启用。 注意：您可以在“添加插件”表单中为每个插件开关。

entries.source: If enabled all beta plugins will be checked for updates each time Obsidian starts. Note: this does not update frozen version plugins.
entries.translated: 如果启用，每次Obsidian启动时都会检查所有测试版插件的更新情况。注意：这不会更新冻结版本的插件。

entries.source: If enabled all beta themes will be checked for updates each time Obsidian starts.
entries.translated: 如果启用，每次Obsidian启动时都会检查所有测试版主题是否有更新。

entries.source: Select latest plugin version by default
If enabled the latest version will be selected by default when adding a new plugin.
entries.translated: 如果启用，添加新插件时将默认选择最新版本。

entries.source: If enabled, plugins with higher app versions will be allowed to be installed. Also it allows desktop-only plugins to be installed on mobile devices.
entries.translated: 如果启用，将允许安装更高应用版本的插件。同时允许在移动设备上安装仅限桌面的插件。

entries.source: Learn more about my work at:
entries.translated: 了解更多关于我的工作：

entries.source: The following is a list of beta plugins added via the command "Add a beta plugin for testing". You can chose to add the latest version or a frozen version. A frozen version is a specific release of a plugin based on its release tag.
entries.translated: 以下是测试版插件列表，可通过命令面板的“添加测试插件”或“添加一个基于发布标签的冻结版本测试插件”的命令快捷添加，其中冻结版本指是基于其发布标签的插件的特定版本。

entries.source: Click the 'Edit' button next to a plugin to change the installed version and the x button next to a plugin to remove it from the list.
entries.translated: 点击插件旁边的“编辑”按钮可更改已安装版本，点击插件旁边的x按钮可将其从列表中移除。

entries.source: Removing from the list does not delete the plugin, this should be done from the Community Plugins tab in Settings.
entries.translated: 从列表中移除不会删除插件，您应该从“设置”中的“社区插件”选项卡中删除它。

entries.source: BRAT will provide popup notifications for its various activities. Turn this off means no notifications from BRAT.
entries.translated: BRAT将为其各种活动提供弹出通知。关闭此选项意味着BRAT不会发出通知。

entries.source: Plugin updates will be logged to a file in the log file.
entries.translated: 插件更新将被记录到日志文件中。

entries.source: Logs will be saved to this file. Don't add .md to the file name.
entries.translated: 日志将被保存到这个文件中。不要在文件名中添加.md后缀。

entries.source: Get a lot more information in the log.
entries.translated: 在日志中获取更多信息。

entries.source: Atomic Bomb level console logging. Can be used for troubleshooting and development.
entries.translated: 极其详尽的控制台日志记录。可用于故障排除和开发。
